    "title_en": "Phase-Selective Amplitude Amplification for Constrained Optimization",
    "abstract_en": "This work introduces a variant of Grover amplitude amplification using stabilizer and blade qubits to improve boosting robustness across objective distributions. We give geometric intuition, example simulations, and discuss limitations. Formal performance bounds and larger-scale validation are left for future research.",
